I haven&#x27;t seen that usage for higher-order components before. This is the pattern I&#x27;ve been following:<p><pre><code>    function decorate (Component) {
      let HigherOrderComponent = React.createClass({
        render () {
          return <Component {...this.props} />
        }
      })

      return HigherOrderComponent
    }
</code></pre>
